>> source: The Essential Mormon Cookbook

In a #large bowl{}, combine @broccoli{1%lb}, @red onion{1%medium}, and @cheddar cheese{1%cup}.

Refrigerate.

Just before serving, stir in @bacon{6%strips}. Add @sunflower seeds (optional){1/2%cup} and @raisins (optional){1/2%cup}.

Pour desired amounts of @broccoli salad dressing{1} over salad. Stir briefly.

Serve the same day.
